{"tid":665382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"震驚全日本！　7歲女童慘死「好青年」手下 先殺後...","createTime":"2018-05-15T01:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T00:35:55.000Z","uid":72009,"like":6,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"154c9a675482d33b99ce768266a6305e7b746c36","tid":665382,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T01:48:32.000Z","msg":"日本這兩日的社會大案，就是一名7歲女童大桃珠生遭人殺害，更被棄屍於鐵軌間被列車輾過分屍，死狀悽慘。而殺害大桃珠生的人，竟然是當地人人稱讚的「好青年」小林遼，他昨日已遭警方逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n據日本《每日新聞》與《產經新聞》報導，大桃珠生在本月初於新潟市西區青山水道的JR越後線鐵軌上，被人發現其屍體，原本一度以為是大桃誤闖鐵軌被輾斃，但事後警方進一步調查發現，大桃在生前是被勒斃殺害，之後再被棄屍於鐵軌，偽裝成交通事故。警方調查後發現，住在大桃家附近的小林遼涉嫌重大，昨日先依棄屍罪將他逮捕。<br />\n現年23歲的小林遼是電器工事師，是某公司雇員，而大桃出事當日，小林遼正好是休假狀態。警方調查發現小林遼涉嫌重大，而且就在上月，小林還扯上對別的女童性騷案件。不過當地人對於小林遼的印象，卻是大不同，包括他的祖父住院時，幾乎都是他前往看護照料，而他平時會幫媽媽繳村內管理費，平常他在工作時，當地居民對他的印象都是「彬彬有禮」。不少人都不相信小林遼是個「人面獸心」的壞人，不認為他會加害幼小孩子。<br />\n警方目前正進一步調查小林遼犯案的動機，以及了解整個犯案過程。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180515/1353918\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180515%2F1353918&d=kJqg1kpVOanmZM9Z9Y77dk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=74c5650c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180515%2F1353918&h=4c2f671a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180515/1353918</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180515/640_01300bd92b558c8280989ebdceb09dfb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180515%2F640_01300bd92b558c8280989ebdceb09dfb.jpg&h=9325d926&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180515/640_036f504f3281000b0a6bbb735697e389.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180515%2F640_036f504f3281000b0a6bbb735697e389.jpg&h=23e1b3e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12899813db7ec8894c50e577d9218c79d0788259","tid":665382,"uid":2389,"like":16,"dislike":432,"score":-416,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T01:52:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"681891548e58da877def0f3d6496409c39f29565","tid":665382,"uid":58140,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T01:53:41.000Z","msg":"日本都幾多恐怖case"},{"pid":"56c4929f5400feec34f2edb63cabda632beaf155","tid":665382,"uid":21423,"like":5,"dislike":28,"score":-23,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T01:54:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36ec9f059f2454da3ea5d516a398ce5b0f84ad52","tid":665382,"uid":38820,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T01:55:08.000Z","msg":"重大犯罪課"},{"pid":"d25d6ec601668dd6dc30857d81d58d16e3d7c76f","tid":665382,"uid":86898,"like":127,"dislike":11,"score":116,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T01:56:05.000Z","msg":"毒撚，成班潛罪犯<br />\n成日蘿莉前蘿莉後，心理變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e8df54e9c1bec762328ba82a10c8238000ca4ee","tid":665382,"uid":72009,"like":20,"dislike":37,"score":-17,"quote":{"pid":"56c4929f5400feec34f2edb63cabda632beaf155","tid":665382,"uid":21423,"like":5,"dislike":28,"score":-23,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T01:54:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T01:56:24.000Z","msg":"條靚妺唔可愛，但唔明點下到手"},{"pid":"0529080cb9b19f7a0c1a8bda121bc89a19ac3621","tid":665382,"uid":9964,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T01:57:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小林<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5882355a3e7b2976a4fc00e052a9c